{
  "description": "A wide shot captures a large flock of shorebirds scattering across a wet sandy beach as waves gently roll in. The birds are predominantly small and white, creating a dynamic sense of movement as they take flight or quickly move along the shoreline. Several larger birds, including one with reddish-brown plumage, are also present within the flock. The background features blurred, foamy waves and a bright, overcast sky. The beach is a flat expanse of wet sand reflecting the sky and birds, adding to the sense of spaciousness and natural beauty. Shadows of the birds are visible on the sand, emphasizing the low angle of the sunlight.",
